name: Kitty Skull
description:
Kitty Skull  > Limited (15/15) 4 Color Print
by: Colby "Sunshine" Nelson

Kitty Skull is one part of my series, Innocence Collection.
The art was designed in 2010 and was pressed this year in 2011.
It was pressed in limited quantities and 15 prints are available.

Enjoy the whimsical mind of my characters and let the emotion
of this piece help you realize the kid inside yourself.

Keep Shining.
Colby "Sunshine" Nelson
Colby Sunshine Art

(Price includes shipping)

name: Flying Panda (limited archival ink print)
description:
Flying Panda (limited archival ink print) 
By: Colby Sunshine Art

This print was printed @ POV Evolving Gallery, LA. It is made with museum quality, archival inks.

These prints are made in limited quantity and are signed/numbered by the artist.

Words from the artist: This print is from my series FLYING PANDAS and this guy will make you feel right
at home with it's vivrant color. It will add a uniqueness to your wall and some emotion to the surround.

Much light and love.
Colby

(Price includes shipping)

name: Stand by the Ones You love
description:
This print was created from my series, Colby Sunshine's Rays of Wisdom.
The print is unique like the artist and exudes emotion on every glance.
It will bring life to any room and kids will smile everytime.

Words from the artist:  As a child I was told, always treat people with the same
feelings you have and always cast wonder and emotions into the things you do.
I hope this piece can make your day and I wish that when it does, you to can 
create your dreams.

Much light and love.
Colby

(Price includes shipping)

name: Bunni Rein (limited archival ink print)
description:
Bunni Rein (limited archival ink print) 
By: Colby Sunshine Art 

Bunni Rein is a limited print that was printed with museum quality archival inks @ POV Evolving Gallery, LA.

These prints are printed in limited quantity and our signed and numbered by the artist.

Words from the artist: This print is from my INNOCENCE SERIES and will bring out the innerchild in any person.
The colors are vivid to add a cozy part in your heart and the characters are a little part of my soul, in which
have a very unique emotion to them.

Much light and love.
Colby

(Price includes shipping)

name: Mystery Sushi Island (Tribute Rolls)
description:
Mystery Sushi Island (Tribute Rolls > Limited, set of 4, Screen prints) > Shredder, Alf, Slimer, and Felix the Cat Rolls 
By: Colby Sunshine Art

These miniature, set of four, Sushi series were produced in limited quantity. They will be signed and numbered by the artist.

Words from the artist: The Mystery Sushi Island (Tribute Rolls) Series is a series of 50 different miniature pieces of cartoon nostalgia added
in with my favorite food, SUSHI.  Two of the best things added into one.
Who could go wrong?  Enjoy these and come back for more.

Much Light and love.
Colby

(Price includes shipping)
